290\" />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Understand Your Business</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Get real time treatment data analysis of your practice. Confidential and secure login. Helps you make better business decisions.</p>\n[/av_content_slide]\n[/av_content_slider]\n[/av_section]\n\n[av_section color=\'alternate_color\' custom_bg=\'\' src=\'\' attachment=\'\' position=\'top left\' repeat=\'no-repeat\' attach=\'scroll\' padding=\'no-padding\' shadow=\'no-shadow\' id=\'home_1\']\n[av_heading heading=\'Key App Features\' tag=\'h2\' color=\'\' style=\'\' padding=\'30\']\n\n[av_one_third first]\n\n[av_icon_box icon=\'71\' position=\'top\' title=\'Treatment Templates\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'no\']\nCreate &amp; save new templates you re-use most often. Or copy previous patient treatments\n[/av_icon_box]\n\n[/av_one_third][av_one_third]\n\n[av_icon_box icon=\'71\' position=\'top\' title=\'Encrypted Cloud Backups\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'no\']\nData is securely backed up to the cloud via 256 AES encryption. Never risk loosing your patient information\n[/av_icon_box]\n\n[/av_one_third][av_one_third]\n\n[av_icon_box icon=\'71\' position=\'top\' title=\'Sync Across Devices\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'no\']\nDo you have multiple devices? Sync your patient treatment history &amp; information across devices\n[/av_icon_box]\n\n[/av_one_third][av_one_third first]\n\n[av_icon_box icon=\'71\' position=\'top\' title=\'Add New Patients\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'no\']\nQuickly create, edit and view patient profiles and keep their information updated\n[/av_icon_box]\n\n[/av_one_third][av_one_third]\n\n[av_icon_box icon=\'71\' position=\'top\' title=\'Patient Treatment History\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'no\']\nAccess a chronological summary of all your previous patient treatments. Copy any previous treatment\n[/av_icon_box]\n\n[/av_one_third][av_one_third]\n\n[av_icon_box icon=\'71\' position=\'top\' title=\'Before &amp; After Photos\' link=\'\' linktarget=\'no\']\nKeep track